level 3:
	spirit seeker
		new ritual only spell list
			beast sense
			speak with animals
	totem spirit:
		when raging:
			friends have melee attack advantage on foes next to you

level 6:
	aspect of the beast
		can track creatures when travelling at fast pace
		can move stealthily when travelling at normal pace

level 10:
	new spell for ritual-only spell list
		commune with nature

level 14:
	totemic attunement:
		when raging:
			if melee attack:
				new bonus action: knock large or smaller enemy prone
		
